New Functionality to Add

Extend the Membership Detail Page (Manage Membership) by introducing a new feature:

Offline Purchase Adjustment

Admins must be able to record jewellery purchases made in-store by customers who are enrolled in a membership plan.

When an offline purchase is recorded:

The system must calculate the total purchase value

Adjust the purchase amount against the amount already paid through installments

Recalculate the remaining payable amount

Recalculate the new EMI amount for the remaining membership duration

This functionality must integrate into the existing membership financial tracking workflow.

