The value must update dynamically whenever items are added or edited.

3. Calculation Logic (Critical Requirement)

The system must follow the below calculation logic.

Definitions:

Plan Amount = Total membership plan value
Monthly EMI = Installment amount
Duration = Total membership duration in months
Installments Paid = Number of installments already paid

Total Paid =
Installments Paid × Monthly EMI

Remaining Months =
Duration − Installments Paid

When an Offline Purchase is Added

Total Purchase Amount =
Sum of all item subtotals

Outstanding Amount =
Total Purchase Amount − Total Paid

New EMI =
Outstanding Amount ÷ Remaining Months

The recalculated EMI represents the amount the customer now needs to pay per month to complete the outstanding balance.

